race.comment: VINALES (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (30.12) at this track in a OPEN. Key player on best and expected to bounce back. IMPRESS HAWKINS (2) has missed the frame at last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in her quick 22.35 win at Mandurah over 400m. Expecting another bold showing. CABIN CREW (6) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when second beaten 3.5 lengths (29.96). Has a win and six places times at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Will give a great sight again. OUR BENSON (3) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.
